[4] Cholera - Worldwide - WHO WER Notifications
Date: Fri 5 Aug 2005
From: Marianne Hopp <mjhopp12@yahoo.com>
Source: WHO Epidemiological Record, 5 Aug 2005 [edited]
<http://www.who.int/wer/2005/wer8031/en>

Notifications of cholera received from 29 Jul to 4 Aug 2005
----------------------------------------------
country / dates / cases / deaths
No new notifications are reported in this issue, but the issue is
dedicated to Cholera, 2004. In total, 101 383 cases were reported,
with 2305 deaths. Of these, 95 560 cases and all but 14 deaths were
from Africa. - Mod.LL]
